Alpha Arts & Science College popularly known as Alpha College is one of the leading and premier self - financing arts and science colleges in Chennai . The college was started in the year 1996 with affiliation to University of Madras . The college is a part of the Alpha Group of Institutions , a group who has more than 4 decades of rich experience in the education industry . The sprawling campus is located in Thundalam , Porur in the suburbs of Chennai right behind Sri Ramachandra Medical College & Research Institute . AASC currently offers undergraduate degrees in the following specializations . AASC also offers Masters degree in the following specializations . 